    <li>Prioritization & planning</li>
    <li>Developing product roadmaps</li>

    <li>Experience leading Agile development teams</li>
    <li>Providing constructive feedback and listening to my teammates</li>
    <li>
      Ability to combine research and design recommendations with technical
      constraints to produce solutions to meet business and user outcomes
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://www.nngroup.com/ux-certification/people/"
        target="_blank"
        style="text-decoration: underline;">UX Master Certification from NN/g</a
      > - 1002824 - Achieved Oct 2023
